         <abstract id="aspace_3b864ece2253c7a3aecb482f263843a1">Correspondence, notebooks, examination questions, photographs and memorabilia almost all related to Collins' student years at Yale. Also included are letters from his years at the Hotchkiss School and memorabilia from his European tour in 1902. The notebooks and other papers of his son-in-law, Jeremiah H. Bartholomew, Jr., from his years at Yale College (1920-1924) are also in the papers.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Collins, Arthur Morris, 1880-1967</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
